A curated list of Optimism RPC endpoints that work well for manual requests:

Public RPCs

https://mainnet.optimism.io

https://optimism.publicnode.com

https://1rpc.io/op

Sepolia Testnet

https://sepolia.optimism.io

Each endpoint supports raw JSON-RPC calls such as:

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "id": 1,
  "method": "eth_getBlockByNumber",
  "params": ["0xA3B24C", false]
}
